en: Detailed commentary on the performance of selected piano works by Bach, Beethoven, Chopin, Liszt and Brahms. This copy includes handwritten notes charting out various concerts that Galston performed as part of his cycle of 40 historical recitals in Germany between 1919 and 1921.
Vorwort -- Bach -- Beethoven -- Chopin -- Liszt -- Brahms -- Anhang -- Register
